<div id="Stripe06">
  <div id="Stripe06_left">
    <!-- p class="h3">ENTERTAINMENT AT YOUR FINGERTIPS</p -->
    <p>Experience the best quality and clarity in the comfort of your own home with the SHARP AQUOS 70&quot; Class (69.5&quot; diag.) LED 4K Smart Android TV with HDR10 (4T-C70BK2UD).  A versatile TV for the modern home entertainment experience, you can easily switch between live programming, streaming channels, and gaming consoles with four HDMI inputs and built-in apps.</p>
    <p>Android TV is an easier way to enjoy the entertainment you love. Stream from your favorite apps, play music and games, cast from any device, and more.  Access to the Google Play Store means you can expand your options with even more compatible apps.  Use your voice to do more on your TV with Google Assistant.  Ask Google to search for the latest blockbuster, stream shows, or open multiplayer games.  Or ask it questions and see the answers right on your TV.</p>
    <p>SHARP AQUOS 70&quot; Class (69.5&quot; diag.) LED 4K Smart Android TV with HDR10 (4T-C70BK2UD) brings you breathtaking clarity, the purest, most vibrant colors, immersive sound, and easy access to all of your favorite media. Immerse yourself in every scene with crisp 20W output audio with surround sound. Included legs and the ability to accept custom mounts (not included) provide flexible placement options. </p>
    
